column5: Went to chuck spoons for salmon off a rivermouth but instead of Salmon a walleye hit my cleo. There used to be many of these fish at this spot in the past, was a bit of a surprise. We got into a few salmon also but the camera battery died and couldn't get a pic of the salmon.       Berge
Pics look a little small. Not sure how to make them bigger.  Berge
Hey Berge nice fish are they from that week you were up there? If so I've got a few up tehre aswell this year nice to see there comeing back.
I think blue/silver cleo will catch anything that swims, sometimes even humans on a packed pier.  Berge
Hey Silvio, yes thats the one i was telling you about. Hey bud, you fishing this weekend?  Berge
